\usemodule{www/slides/html5?htmlfive}

\sn{html?HTML} was created in 1990 and standardized in version 4 in
1997~\cite{RagHor:html98}. Since then the \sn{WWW} has evolved considerably from a
web of static \sns{web-page?web page} to a \sr{WWW}{Web} in which highly
dynamic \sns{web-page?web page} become user interfaces for web-based
applications and even mobile applets. \sn{htmlfive?HTML5} standardized the
necessary infrastructure in 2014~\cite{W3C:html5}.
